---
import WhatsAppButton from './WhatsAppButton.astro';
---
<section
  class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-breath to-brand-clinical/15 border-t border-brand-authority/10"
  aria-labelledby="cierre-heading"
>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 lg:gap-14 items-center">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-[42%] flex justify-center lg:justify-start shrink-0">
        <img
          src="/dr-liber-cierre.png"
          alt="Dr. Liber Acosta en consultorio"
          class="w-full max-w-sm lg:max-w-none rounded-2xl shadow-xl ring-1 ring-brand-authority/10 object-cover aspect-[4/5] sm:aspect-[3/4] lg:aspect-[4/5] max-h-[420px] lg:max-h-[480px]"
          width="480"
          height="600"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="w-full lg:flex-1 flex flex-col items-center lg:items-end text-center lg:text-right">
        <h2
          id="cierre-heading"
          class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-brand-authority mb-8 lg:max-w-xl"
        >
          Si tenés síntomas frecuentes que afectan tu vida diaria, es momento de evaluarlo
          correctamente.
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-base text-brand-technical/75 lg:max-w-md">
          Respuesta rápida y gestión de turnos centralizada.
        </p>
        <WhatsAppButton>Agendar ahora por WhatsApp</WhatsAppButton>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
